name: Trooper Davin Felth (V)
Lore: 'Dispatched to Tatooine to apprehend renegade droids fleeing the Tantive IV. Suspected to have misgivings about Imperial methods. Allegedly shot his commander in the back.',
Text: 'During your control phase, may take (or lose 1 Force to retrieve) one Local Trouble or Look Sir, Droids into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Opponent may not fire weapons during Local Trouble battles.',
